node.text:
This is an amazing mask ! Highly recommend you to add it to your natural hair routine ! My hair felt so soft, moisturized and shiny after ! 

I applied the aloe to my hair ( you can blend it to get more aloe )

I then added some jbco. 100% natural from @rootedtreasure just for extra shine and moisture + it has a lot of great benefits 

Then I made sure to massage it into my scalp. Fun fact. Aloe is great for dandruff and troubled scalp problems ! 

I allowed it to sit in my hair for about 30 mins. 

Then I rinsed it out and styled as usual 

A more detailed video is on my channel (link in bio) 
#naturalhair #naturalhairmask #naturalhaircommunity #naturalhairjourney
